Class BookCopy

  • java.lang.Object
    • cz.muni.fi.pa165.library.entity.BookCopy

  • @Entity
public class BookCopy
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity class representing BookCopy in the library system. A bookCopy is exactly one (printed) copy of a book. Making a loan in a system is based on this entity.
